metadata.description: Generative MIGHTY METAS LOVE: ALL OCCASIONS. This Mighty Metas Love greeting cards collection allows a sender to have a powerful message of love delivered to their recipient. Super adorable, this generative art greeting card collection contains eight messages of love to let your recipient know they're special to you. MESSAGE: Issued at random with possible messages: (1) I'll Always Fight for Us, (2) You're My Queen, (3) I'd Face Any Enemy for You, (4) I Love You, (5) I'd Fight for You, (6) You're My King, (7) With You, I Am Invincible, and (8) I Love You More. The End. I Win.
metadata.name: MIGHTY METAS LOVE #1
